OL,3,CThousands of Muslims mark Eid al-Adh
OL,4,Cat The Mubarak Mosque in Farnham
OL,6,FImam, Farhad Ahmad said, "It's an
OL,7,Fextremely important. You wear your
OL,8,Fbest clothes. Children take time off
OL,9,Fschool, people take time off work, you
OL,10,Fcome early morning to the Mosque to
OL,11,Fpray.
OL,13,F"It's a day to spend with family
OL,14,Fenjoying each other's company.
OL,16,F"My family, we are sacrificing an
OL,17,Fanimal in Africa so it helps people
OL,18,Fthere, sometimes people haven't had
OL,19,Fmeat for a whole year so this is the
OL,20,Ffirst time they probably get to have
OL,21,Fmeat."
