OL,3,CThousands of Muslims mark Eid al-Adh
OL,4,Cat The Mubarak Mosque in Farnham
OL,6,F"It reminds us of the sacrifice that
OL,7,FProphet Abraham and his son, Prophet
OL,8,FIshmael said.
OL,10,F"All these true stories are there to
OL,11,Fremind us as Muslims that we have a
OL,12,Fpurpose in life.
OL,14,F"One is to follow the commandments and
OL,15,Four duty god but secondly, and more
OL,16,Fimportantly, is our duties to our
OL,17,Ffellow human beings.
